LAGOS  – Logitech has taken sound out of the equation with the introduction of Logitech® M220 Silent Wireless Mouse – their first quietest mouse ever. With the mouse, there’s no need to disturb others while users stay productive as it offers a quiet experience for the users and those around them The mouse provides a wireless connection up to 33-feet away with 128-bit encryption between the mouse and the receiver. It also has Logitech Advanced Optical Tracking designed for smooth and precise moves on almost any surface. The Logitech M220 Silent offers an 18-month battery life with auto sleep feature and an ambidextrous, portable design. The ambidextrous design offers more comfort and precision. With the unique mouse, users can now start enjoying the sound of silence with the M220 Silent mouse by purchasing it from local market retailers in Lagos and other parts of the country.